verbose_text: The results demonstrate that low concentrations of NVP-BEZ235 (1-5 nM) significantly inhibited the expression of p110alpha (1 nM; P = 0.0021), p-Akt (5 nM; P = 0.0043) and p-p70S6K (5 nM; P = 0.0065).
